Package: EMPAFunctionAnalysis
Title: EMPA Level 3 Estuary Dashboard Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Brooke", "Fulkerson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "placeholder@example.com")
Description: Data loading, cleaning, scoring, and visualization functions for
    the Estuary MPA (EMPA) Level 3 dashboard. Covers vegetation condition,
    CRAM assessments, invasive species severity, ruggedness, sea level rise
    vulnerability, and buffer land cover analyses across 16 California
    estuary sites.
